1. Svi su* srećni. (Everyone is happy.)
2. Oni su* veoma zainteresovani za naučna istraživanja. (They are very interested in scientific research.)
3. Ona je* bila suočena sa teškim situacijama. (She was faced with difficult situations.)
4. Oni su* se trudili da postignu svoje ciljeve. (They were trying to achieve their goals.)
5. To su* moji prijatelji. (Those are my friends.)
6. Oni su* vam spremni pomoći. (They are ready to help you.)
7. To su* moje misli. (Those are my thoughts.)
8. Ona je* bila uspešna u svojim nastojanjima. (She was successful in her endeavors.)